		<h2 style="font-size: 40px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: white">About Prote-Con</h2>
		<p style="font-size: 20px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: white">Prote-Con acts as an integrated website, combining multiple tools for protein conservation explorations. Our objective is to expedite protein sequence analysis, by providing all-in-one feature. Tools: ClustalO, EMBOSS patmatmotifs, EMBOSS plotcon and IQTREE. Data retrieved via Prote-Con are from NCBI Protein database.</p>
